Class ModelFactoryImpl

java.lang.Object
cat.uvic.teknos.dam.kamika.model.impl.ModelFactoryImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
ModelFactory
public class ModelFactoryImpl extends Object implements ModelFactory
Implementation of the ModelFactory interface. Provides methods to create new instances of model entities.
